p><p><br></p><p>2 Pouches = Two month's supply for 5-8 chickens</p><p><br></p><p>3 Pouches = Three month's supply for 9-12 chickens</p><p><br></p><p>4 Pouches = Three month's supply for 13-20 chickens<br><br>5 Pouches = 4 month's supply for 21-25 chickens</p></span></div></div></div><div data-state="active" data-orientation="vertical" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-:R52hnr2:-trigger-5aad23a3-e56c-46f5-a9d0-6568ed075c092" id="radix-:R52hnr2:-content-5aad23a3-e56c-46f5-a9d0-6568ed075c092" tabindex="0" style="display:contents;animation-duration:0s"><div data-rid="4cb2f56f-1004-48a2-a2e9-d43f1148324b" class="r-1ir22ew"><div data-rid="553841ce-f630-4e17-a556-473ec0ae9e48" class="r-1ov0s3k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>🐜 <strong>Helps repel mites, lice, flies & mosquitoes naturally</strong><br>with our powerful mint, rosemary & thyme essential-oil blend</p><p><br></p><p>🌿 <strong>Smells amazing & keeps your coop fresh for weeks</strong><br>so tending your flock feels cleaner and more enjoyable every day<br><br>🐔 <strong>Creates a calmer, low-stress coop environment</strong><br>so your hens feel safer, more comfortable, and at ease<br><br>🫧 <strong>Promotes a cleaner, healthier living space</strong><br>by reducing strong odors that attract unwanted pests<br><br>🇺🇸 <strong>Made in the USA with 100% natural, flock-safe ingredients</strong><br>trusted by chicken owners who want a safer alternative to chemicals</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3337deb2-705c-4a4d-b1ec-2dfcf9cb8e3b" class="r-u1gog0" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="2020fc32-c150-4ee9-aad9-947f6b75826b" class="r-pkrc32" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="19068ff1-0b5f-452c-8bdd-cdc7a0290750" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R36hnr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1jto9sp"><div data-rid="9d9c5660-325b-40f9-b984-c2368d70a778" class="r-16iepwy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is this just for the smell, or does it help my flock in other ways?</p></span></div><div data-rid="134fb074-5927-4256-9a42-b26806a87b73" class="r-1u661l4" aria-hidden="true"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-chevron-down" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: auto" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R36hnr2:"><div data-rid="f60d469d-d4b8-4427-91c5-d428da11cd15" class="r-154mij"><div data-rid="723d7a1d-9b81-4b81-ac23-6380c450435b" class="r-1pobgqv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Both of our scents smell incredible. They don’t just minimize odors—they help create a calming environment for your flock while naturally reducing the chances of pests entering your coop.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="bfffd65a-9add-4f84-8ea0-318467b2434b" class="r-19hu24g" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="0f462013-6efe-4d97-8731-ee721fbac4e8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R56hnr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-l4vxk8"><div data-rid="fe4a4a45-9b9e-4086-99d2-e02a5f20a3ea" class="r-wkb05d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I use this in my cat litter box or other animals that require bedding? </p></span></div><div data-rid="94604e7e-edad-4d0f-8ecc-e48f0f1f9a17" class="r-mov32x" aria-hidden="true"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-chevron-down" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: auto" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R56hnr2:"><div data-rid="8a282ef1-10a6-4391-97df-a53ef60f38c8" class="r-1t0zk98"><div data-rid="0c6f525f-6001-4867-8b95-668318d784ea" class="r-790l4u alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes you 100% can use this in cat litter boxes and any other animal that requires bedding. Keep in mind that each pack is for a 4X4 foot area so if you are using it in smaller spaces portion it out correctly. </p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a02391ba-1889-450c-9a38-88fff4d9fe12" class="r-gsb369" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="cda3e9d4-0a8d-41c9-a5f9-2a84100ede14" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R76hnr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-7qanvz"><div data-rid="78b4dfde-7b88-490a-a4bd-c253d56cb4f6" class="r-m52smi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What ingredients are in Coop Refreshers? </p></span></div><div data-rid="f2b4dfcb-4c19-4dac-a35b-21159f2be9cb" class="r-1yw1qbg" aria-hidden="true"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-chevron-down" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: auto" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R76hnr2:"><div data-rid="526f1c07-88f6-4e5e-929e-af03f7806cff" class="r-ms0lte"><div data-rid="2be71736-107b-466d-9c8f-f018053cb769" class="r-1hp6u9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The primary ingredient in our Coop Refreshers is a blend of essential oils, carefully coated onto small vermiculite pellets. It’s completely safe for both chickens and humans.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1365cc60-0142-4538-88eb-ce